videos.headline: Fields floats in a TD to Olave
videos.description: Justin Fields matriculates the Buckeyes down the field and caps off the drive with a 20-yard touchdown pass to Chris Olave.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fields floats in a TD to Olave) 2019/10/18

videos.headline: Young disrupts Northwestern's opening drive with a sack
videos.description: Chase Young takes down Northwestern QB Aidan Smith to increase his sack total to 9.5 for the season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Young disrupts Northwestern's opening drive with a sack) 2019/10/18

videos.headline: Dobbins' 68-yard run sets up his 5-yard TD
videos.description: J.K. Dobbins breaks some tackles and gets free for a 68-yard run. The next play he would sprint outside for the five-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dobbins' 68-yard run sets up his 5-yard TD) 2019/10/18

videos.headline: Fields and Olave link up for another TD
videos.description: Justin Fields sells the play action and finds Chris Olave for the eight-yard touchdown, and Olave's second score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fields and Olave link up for another TD) 2019/10/18

videos.headline: Fields keeps the rout going with his 4th TD
videos.description: Justin Fields continues his dominant performance in the second half as he throws a 23-yard touchdown to Austin Mack.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fields keeps the rout going with his 4th TD) 2019/10/18

videos.headline: Freshman Teague explodes for 73-yard TD
videos.description: Master Teague III bolts to the end zone for a 73-yard score and 52-3 Ohio State lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Freshman Teague explodes for 73-yard TD) 2019/10/18 ESHEET
